sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant G7 as G7 Suivi
    participant K as Kafka vehicule-positions
    participant C as G7VehiclePositionKafkaConsumer
    participant V as KafkaContractValidator
    participant L as SupervisionLogService
    participant ES as CoordinationEventService
    G7->>K: publish position JSON
    K->>C: message
    C->>V: validateG7Position
    alt invalide
        C->>L: WARN payload rejete
    else valide
        C->>L: INFO KAFKA-G7
        opt deviation
            C->>ES: create DEVIATION
        end
    end
